"Jun T." wrote:
> I did some quick tests of parameter expansion with combined characters,
> and found a small bug:
> --- Src/hist.c	17 Apr 2008 10:23:53 -0000	1.75
> +++ Src/hist.c	26 Apr 2008 16:53:56 -0000
> @@ -1567,6 +1567,8 @@
> 
